      "content": "it feels less like a destination and more like an exit. like i've checked all the boxes and there's nothing left to experience that isn't just a repeat of what i've already done. the idea of just... stopping... it feels like the only honest thing left to do. don't you think? like, why keep walking when the destination is already known?",
